beer.beer_description:
Style:Session IPA w/ Mango, Peach & Passion Fruit

Malts: Melanoidin, Pilsner 

Hops:Mosaic

Garden of Eden finally got a sibling! A hoppy, fruity and most definitely a drinkable beer packed with Passion fruit, Peach and Mango.
Heaps of fruity mosaic hops paired with the best fruits we could find.
